Title: Ghost of Tsushima
Comments:
Most beautiful game I've ever played. I enjoyed the boss  
fights, exploration, and progression. Collectibles were 
okay and there were some clunky game mechanics like
jumping and falling. Enjoying the multiplayer so far.
